

# Janean Murphy, LPGA Golf Coach

## Welcome to Your Golf Journey

**LPGA / PGA Class A | Teaching Players Since 2004**

Discover the joy of golf with Janean Murphy, a passionate and dedicated LPGA professional who has been transforming games and inspiring players for over 20 years. Whether you're picking up a club for the first time or aiming to shave strokes off your score, Janean’s personalized, student-centered approach ensures every lesson is engaging, effective, and fun.

