## Why Choose Janean?

**Tailored Instruction for Every Golfer**  
I believe every golfer is unique. That’s why I take the time to understand your goals, body mechanics, and learning style to create lessons that fit *you*. From beginners to low-handicap players, men, women, juniors, or adults, I’m here to help you:

- Master your full swing, short game, and putting  
- Develop on-course strategy and mental toughness  
- Find the right equipment for your game  
- Most importantly, have fun playing golf!  

Whether you’re dreaming of a casual 9 holes with friends or preparing for competitive play, I’ll guide you every step of the way with enthusiasm and expertise.

